    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="蓝桥杯题目练习"><a href="#蓝桥杯题目练习" class="headerlink" title="蓝桥杯题目练习"></a>蓝桥杯题目练习</h1><h2 id="2019问题"><a href="#2019问题" class="headerlink" title="2019问题"></a>2019问题</h2><p>题目：</p><blockquote><p>数字中含“2”、“0”、“1”、“9”的数字称为”王瀚弘数“，求出0到2019所有王瀚弘数的和。</p></blockquote><p>刚拿到这道题我的第一想法是</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">f</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> a)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>判断a是否为王瀚弘数<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> sum=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="hljs-number">2020</span>;i++)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(f(i))<br>&#123;<br>sum+=i;<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>,sum);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这是我的第一想法</p><p>但是在实现的过程中发现f函数实现起来过于复杂</p><p>于是我改变了思路</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> g,s,b,q,sum=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(q=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;q&lt;=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;q++)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(b=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;b&lt;<span class="hljs-number">10</span>;b++)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(s=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;s&lt;<span class="hljs-number">10</span>;s++)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(g=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;g&lt;<span class="hljs-number">10</span>;g++)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> a;<br>a=q*<span class="hljs-number">1000</span>+b*<span class="hljs-number">100</span>+s*<span class="hljs-number">10</span>+g;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(a==<span class="hljs-number">2020</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">goto</span> end;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>((q==<span class="hljs-number">2</span>||q==<span class="hljs-number">0</span>||q==<span class="hljs-number">1</span>||q==<span class="hljs-number">9</span>)&amp;&amp;(b==<span class="hljs-number">2</span>||b==<span class="hljs-number">0</span>||b==<span class="hljs-number">1</span>||b==<span class="hljs-number">9</span>)&amp;&amp;(s==<span class="hljs-number">2</span>||s==<span class="hljs-number">0</span>||s==<span class="hljs-number">1</span>||s==<span class="hljs-number">9</span>)&amp;&amp;(g==<span class="hljs-number">2</span>||g==<span class="hljs-number">0</span>||g==<span class="hljs-number">1</span>||g==<span class="hljs-number">9</span>)) <br>&#123;<br>sum+=a;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>,a);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br>end: <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>,sum);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样一来免去了实现f函数</p><h2 id="矩形切割"><a href="#矩形切割" class="headerlink" title="矩形切割"></a>矩形切割</h2><p>没啥想法，直接暴力来吧</p><h2 id="年号字串"><a href="#年号字串" class="headerlink" title="年号字串"></a>年号字串</h2><blockquote><p>A代表1，B代表2······Z代表26，AA代表27。问：2019对应什么?</p></blockquote><p>这题也比较简单</p><p>将其转换为26进制数即可</p><h2 id="质数问题"><a href="#质数问题" class="headerlink" title="质数问题"></a>质数问题</h2><p>这种题核心就是一个函数</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">isp</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> a)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;i&lt;a;i++) <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(a%i==<span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>用它来判断一个数是否为质数</p><h2 id="最大降雨量"><a href="#最大降雨量" class="headerlink" title="最大降雨量"></a>最大降雨量</h2><p>题目</p><blockquote><p>49个数，分成7组，去出每组的中位数a1、a2···a7，再取七个中位数的中位数A。问题：A最大为多少？</p></blockquote><p>有3个中位数大于A</p><p>设为a1、a2、a3</p><p>共有九个数分别大于a1、a2、a3</p><p>所以要有12个数大于A</p><p>所以A最大为37</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
